{"tid":2509474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保安局：已提醒入境處可於帳委會反駁 勿再出聲","createTime":"2021-04-29T12:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T13:12:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":66,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"7aff360966b685ae3e0af3fea2f97b229b3221e3","tid":2509474,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"保安局：提醒入境處避免公開爭辯<br />\n<br />\n入境處和審計署就審計報告隔空罵戰。保安局晚上指，已就入境處昨日的新聞公報，向入境處提醒應該遵從在報告提交至立法會期間，避免作出公開爭辯的共識，以確保聆訊公平順利進行。而在政府帳目委員會跟進審計署報告時，入境處到時可作交代，保安局目前不作進一步評論。<br />\n<br />\n日前最新一份審計報告，批評入境處追查假結婚個案力度不足，入境處昨日深夜罕有反駁，形容一些不懂刑事調查的人胡亂批評，嚴重破壞處方專業形象。審計署下午再作回應，引用政府財務通告指，現階段不論是局長、部門首長、公共機構主管抑或屬下人員，都應避免公開反駁審計結果。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389482&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=afc92668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389482</a>"},{"pid":"3b979cea3af6562f1bf4a79ddc3dbe106031430f","tid":2509474,"uid":276592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e12b9c2cd77d41e150067ac3d3682a6d4324ea","tid":2509474,"uid":60924,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揭起晒比人睇"},{"pid":"ff72e094e2efa3b6c4662dd6274b7cf9bd1b35e1","tid":2509474,"uid":132572,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾入境處抵比人串"},{"pid":"defb2a78202e39cde81fecdd02136ef1158ac9d0","tid":